@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About Us";
}

<style>
    body {
        background-image: url('../image/WallpaperBackground.jpg');
    }

    .about-page .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    .about-page .about-section,
    .about-page .vision-section,
    .about-page .mission-section,
    .about-page .values-section {
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .about-page h2 {
        color: #333;
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .about-page h3 {
        color: #555;
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .about-page p {
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #666;
    }

    .about-page .values-section ul {
        list-style-type: disc;
        padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .about-page .values-section li {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #666;
    }

    .about-page .about-section,
    .about-page .vision-section,
    .about-page .mission-section,
    .about-page .values-section {
        background-color: #9FC5E8;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
</style>

<link href="~/css/site.css" rel="stylesheet" />

<div class="container about-page">
    <div class="about-section">
        <h2>Welcome to Khumalo Craft Emporium</h2>
        <p>Khumalo Craft Emporium is a global e-commerce platform dedicated to showcasing handcrafted products from artisans worldwide. Our mission is to connect these talented artisans with a discerning audience, providing a platform for them to showcase their unique creations to the world.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="vision-section">
        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>At Khumalo Craft Emporium, we envision a world where traditional craftsmanship thrives and artisans are celebrated for their talent and creativity. We are committed to promoting cultural heritage, sustainability, and fair trade practices in the artisanal community.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mission-section">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>Our mission is to create a global marketplace that empowers artisans, fosters cultural exchange, and enriches the lives of both creators and consumers. We strive to provide a platform where artisans can showcase their craftsmanship, gain recognition for their work, and earn a sustainable income.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="values-section">
        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Quality:</strong> We are committed to offering high-quality, handmade products that reflect the skill and dedication of our artisans.</li>
            <li><strong>Diversity:</strong> We celebrate diversity in artistry and culture, embracing the rich tapestry of traditions from around the world.</li>
            <li><strong>Sustainability:</strong> We prioritize sustainability and ethical practices, supporting artisans who use environmentally-friendly materials and production methods.</li>
            <li><strong>Community:</strong> We believe in fostering a supportive community where artisans, customers, and enthusiasts can connect, learn, and grow together.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

